Miguel Antonio Matos (amụrụ na Septemba 1, 1983), nke a maara dịka Antonio Fresco, bụ ónyé American DJ, onye na-emepụta ihe ndekọ na ónyé redio. Ọ bụ ónyé Afro-Latino nke Dominican na Puerto Rican.
Fresco bụ ónyé bụbu ónyé redio na DJ maka ụlọ ọrụ redio kachasị elu, 97.9 The Beat na Dallas, Texas. N'oge ọ na-arụ ọrụ na redio, Antonio agbaala ọtụtụ ndị ama ama dịka ndị na-eti egwu Nelly, B.o

ajụjụ ọnụ.B., na onye bụbu otu ụmụ nwanyị, OMG Girlz. Mgbè ọ bi na Dallas, na ikuku, o jiri aha M-Squared mee ihe. N'ọnwa Nọvemba afọ 2011, Fresco mepụtara ma kwado cypher a na-akpọ M-Squared Presents The Understanding DFW Cypher nke gosipụtara onwé ya na onye omenkà egwu isii, gụnyere B-Hamp, site na mpaghara Dallas Fort Worth. E gosipụtara vidiyo egwu nke ónyé na-ede akwụkwọ na mbipụta mpaghara Dallas, D Magazine N'ọnwa Eprel afọ 2014, Dallas Weekly họpụtara ya dịka Best DJ.
Fresco sonyeere ónyé na-agụ egwu Jonn Hart na onye na-emepụta Clayton William iji wepụta egwu egwu a na-akpọ Blow It
Blow A tọhapụrụ ya ọzọ n'okpuru aha ónyé na-ese ihe Hella Louud (otu nke Hart na William mejupụtara) na-egosi Antonio Fresco.
A mụrụ Miguel Antonio Matos na Septemba 1, 1983 na Silver Spring, Maryland. A zụlitere ya na Baltimore, Maryland, site n'aka nné ya, ónyé bụ onye Puerto Rican si New York.
